# HUD::THEFEED_SET_SCRIPTED_MENU_HEIGHT

## Summary
Tell the feed system how high the scripted menu is so it doesn't overlap it

## Parameters
* **FLOAT** scriptedMenuHeight:
The height of the scripted menu.
Pass 0.0 to revert back to normal.
